              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5993310411260167194">Though I can&apos;t quite put my finger on why, this story just didn&apos;t manage to draw me in as much as the other novels by Kamila Shamsie I&apos;ve read. Perhaps it&apos;s just a case of too many characters, none of whom I felt any attachment to.</span>
  <span id="freeText5993310411260167194" style="display:none">Though I can't quite put my finger on why, this story just didn't manage to draw me in as much as the other novels by Kamila Shamsie I've read. Perhaps it's just a case of too many characters, none of whom I felt any attachment to.</span>
